# BillSplitter App
Developed by Marcus Lee

BillSplitter is a mobile app designed to simplify group bill sharing by providing fast, accurate, and transparent expense-splitting features. Whether you are dining out, traveling, or managing shared household costs, this app eliminates the confusion and frustration that usually comes with splitting payments among multiple people.

